The Clara 3 Piece Nursery set includes a cot bed, dresser, changer, and wardrobe. The Clara Cot Bed has an adaptable design that grows with your little one. Suitable from birth to five years, the cot bed has 3 mattress base positions that can be lowered as your baby grows and develops. Once they’ve outgrown the cot bed, you can easily convert it to a stylish toddler bed. Suitable for 0-5 years 3 different mattress base positions Converts from cot bed to a toddler bed Requires a 140 x 70cm cot bed mattress sold separately Fully certified and accredited testing to BS EN 716:2017, BS 8509:2008+A1:2011 5-year warranty against manufacturing defects. The warranty period is effective from the day of purchase Self-assembly required: Yes The Clara Dresser Changer is a 2-in-1 nursery must-have, providing both storage and a changing station in one stylish product. This nursery dresser has 3 roomy drawers, perfect for storing everything from nappies and wipes to baby sleepsuits and muslins. With a removable changing station, Clara can be converted to a standalone dresser once your little one is out of nappies. The changing top is suitable up until 11kg approx 12 months Changing mat sold separately Lay the mat on the top surface within the retaining barriers Removable changing station Features 3 spacious drawers Self-assembly required: Yes Fully certified and accredited testing to FIRA FRQG C001 & C004 5-year warranty against manufacturing defects The warranty period is effective from the day of purchase. The Clara Nursery Wardrobe has ample room to keep your baby’s clothes organised. This double wardrobe has 2 removable hanging rails for keeping their tiny outfits neat and tidy. Inside the wardrobe is a deep shelf, perfect for storing baby bedding or blankets. Plus, the Clara Wardrobe also has a roomy drawer providing extra storage. 2 removable hanging rails 1 internal adjustable shelf 1 drawer Self-assembly required: Yes Fully certified and accredited testing to BS EN 12221:2008+A1:2013, FIRA FRQG C001 & C004 5-year warranty against manufacturing defects.
